# Validating Sonar Analysis and Quality Gates

This GitHub action is used to fail GitHub workflow in case Quality Gates failed. This GitHub action expect the following required parametes:

|-------------|----------|
| Parameters  | Required | 
|-------------|----------|
| sonar_url   |   yes    |
| sonar_token |   yes    |
| project_key |   yes    |
| branch      |   yes    |
|-------------|----------|

